30
00:08:50,400 --> 00:08:51,520
Four thousand baht.

31
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,120
Four thousand baht.

32
00:08:53,160 --> 00:08:53,840
Yes

33
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:05,200
