35
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:10,440
Yes.

36
00:09:22,880 --> 00:09:26,200
If you like it, I'll buy it for you.

37
00:09:30,680 --> 00:09:33,320
Pick up the first lottery ticket from the bottom left row.

38
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:49,120
Oh, if it doesn't win,

39
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:54,120
you'll be a ghost who's both a thief and a scammer!

40
00:09:55,640 --> 00:09:57,440
Just trust me.

41
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:01,240
