42
00:10:03,680 --> 00:10:08,360
Just like my feelings for you—

43
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:11,360
It’s stable and unwavering.

44
00:10:15,920 --> 00:10:17,320
I love you,

45
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:25,280
whether you're Wiranwee or Navee.

46
00:11:08,160 --> 00:11:10,160
