47
00:11:20,800 --> 00:11:22,520
Is it about us?

48
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:31,000
You don't have to worry about anything.

49
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:36,680
Even if the sky falls and the earth crumbles, I won't let anyone separate us,

50
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:41,720
because I love you.

51
00:11:45,840 --> 00:11:48,480
